<!-- Core Values -->
<section id="core-values" class="core-values">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Core Values</h2>
    <p>At C.O.O.L. Enrichment, our approach revolves around fostering curiosity, respect for nature, and experiential learning. We are committed to instilling a sense of wonder and appreciation for the environment, encouraging students to become responsible stewards of the Earth. Our core values emphasize the importance of hands-on exploration, environmental awareness, and cultivating a lifelong passion for outdoor education.</p>
    <p>C.O.O.L. Enrichment provides students with outdoor experiences in Nature Journaling, hiking, science exploration, and species identifications. We are dedicated to fostering a deep connection with nature and empowering students through experiential learning in the great outdoors. Our focus is on promoting environmental stewardship and cultivating a love for the natural world.</p>
  </div>
</section>

